100 REMark read the documentation in the help subdirectory
110 REMark also for the 'current_line' keyword
120 REMark lrespr cline_bin before using this prog.
130 REMark if the "restoring" message always refers to 0, then you haven't loaded cline_bin
140 :
150 DEFine PROCedure p
160   delete_all_targets
170 END DEFine p
180 :
190 DEFine PROCedure delete_all_targets
200 REMark this deletes all targets and all intermediary targets, thus forcing
210 REMark a complete rebuild. Caution, this also deletes all lib and rel files
220   delete_files_with_extension "rel","dev8_",1
230   delete_files_with_extension "err","dev8_",1
240   delete_files_with_extension "map","dev8_",1
250   delete_files_with_extension "log","dev8_",1
260   COPY_O dev8_minerva_inc_ERR_copy,  dev8_minerva_inc_ERR
270   COPY_O dev8_keys_err_copy,  dev8_keys_err
280   generic
290   atari
300   gold
310   q40
320   qxl
330 END DEFine delete_all_targets
